name: Fuerte Robusto
additionalNotes: Manufactured by Plasencia in Honduras, La Floridita Fuerte is available in three sizes, Churchill (7 x 50), Toro (6 x 50), and Robusto (5 x 50). The cigars have a medium to full-bodied blend of Nicaraguan Esteli and Jalapa Habano plus Honduran Jamastran Habano longfillers, Nicaraguan Jalapa binders, and Habano Viso wrappers.
